cool medium-lengthed map I made recently. 

fairly technical map. 1:40s ~ 2:00 long. This will probably be my last map for awhile unless there is a mapping competition. I hope you all enjoy this one.

There are two bonuses. Bonus 1 is technical and around 40s. Bonus 2 is short and strafey, around 8-10 seconds.
